title: New India Sweets and Spices
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian grocery and deli. The deli is in the back of the store. There is an a la carte menu and a steamtable with ready made hot South Indian food: currys, samosas, chaat. Corn oil used in most dishes. Also some sweets and savory snacks sold by weight. Has a small table inside for seating. Street parking.
